Ernest R. Verebelyi

Age : 69Public asset : 962,554 USDLinked companies :  Columbus McKinnon Corp. 





Summary 



Mr. Ernest R. Verebelyi is Chairman at Columbus McKinnon Corp.Mr. Verebelyi was previously employed as Independent Director by CH Energy Group, Inc., President by Terex Corp., Executive Vice President-Operations by General Signal Corp., and Executive Vice President-Special Products Division by Emerson Electric Co.



